@startuml
title Sequence 05 — Service Registration & Discovery via Eureka

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #2E7D32
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
skinparam participantBorderColor #2E7D32
skinparam participantFontStyle bold
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #A5D6A7
skinparam noteBorderColor #F57F17
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF9C4
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

participant "IAM Service\n:8081"      as IAM
participant "Ledger Service\n:8083"   as LEDGER
participant "Account Service\n:8082"  as ACC
participant "Eureka Server\n:8761"    as EUREKA
participant "API Gateway\n:8080"      as GW
actor       Customer

== Startup: All Services Register ==

IAM    -> EUREKA : Register { name: iam-service,     host: iam-service,     port: 8081 }
EUREKA --> IAM   : 204 Registered

LEDGER -> EUREKA : Register { name: ledger-service,  host: ledger-service,  port: 8083 }
EUREKA --> LEDGER : 204 Registered

ACC    -> EUREKA : Register { name: account-service, host: account-service, port: 8082 }
EUREKA --> ACC   : 204 Registered

GW     -> EUREKA : Register { name: api-gateway,     host: gateway,         port: 8080 }
EUREKA --> GW    : 204 Registered

note over EUREKA
  Heartbeat every 30 seconds.
  Services evicted after 90 seconds
  of missing heartbeat.
end note

== Runtime: Customer Initiates a Transfer ==

Customer -> GW     : POST /api/transactions/transfer

GW -> EUREKA       : Lookup "iam-service"
EUREKA --> GW      : [{ host: iam-service, port: 8081 }]

GW -> IAM          : Validate JWT (load-balanced)
IAM --> GW         : 200 OK

GW -> EUREKA       : Lookup "ledger-service"
EUREKA --> GW      : [{ host: ledger-service, port: 8083 }]

GW -> LEDGER       : POST /internal/transfer

LEDGER -> EUREKA   : Lookup "account-service"
EUREKA --> LEDGER  : [{ host: account-service, port: 8082 }]

LEDGER -> ACC      : GET /internal/accounts/{id}
ACC --> LEDGER     : Account details

LEDGER --> GW      : 200 Transfer Completed
GW --> Customer    : 200 Transfer Successful
@enduml
